{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解弹簧测力计的结构，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">练习使用弹簧测力计</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在弹性限度内，弹簧的伸长量与弹簧所受拉力成正比。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计、钩码</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.观察弹簧测力计，确定它的量程和分度值。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.检查</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计的指针是否指在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">零刻度线上，如果不在，应该</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把指针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调节</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">零刻度线上</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.拉动弹簧测力计的挂钩，分别使指针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分别指到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1N<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">N<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">N<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">位置，观察弹簧长度的变化。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.把一个钩码或几个钩</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">码悬挂在弹簧测力计的挂钩上，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量钩</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">码对弹簧测力计的拉力。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计使用时需要注意以下几点：</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.&ldquo;察&rdquo;：观察弹簧测力计的最大量程和最小分度值。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.&ldquo;调&rdquo;：将弹簧测力计的指针调零。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.&ldquo;测&rdquo;：测量读数，没有估读，靠近哪条刻度线读哪条。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉力要沿弹簧的中心轴线方向施加在弹簧秤上。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观察指针示数视线要与刻度线垂直</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}